entity.name: Day 9
entity.description: John Inverdale presents coverage of the fourth round of Roland-Garros as the world's best tennis players meet in Paris. Match analysis is from four-time Grand Slam champion Jim Courier, former French players Fabrice Santoro and Marion Bartoli, Andy Murray's former coach, Mark Petchey, and former British number ones Anne Keothavong and Sam Smith. Commentary from Nick Mullins and Jonathan Overend with Celina Hinchcliffe reporting.
